........................................................................................ 80\r\nThe Build.................................................................................................. 81\r\nThe Sketch............................................................................................. 82\r\n\r\ni x • C o n t e n t s i n D e ta i l\r\n\r\n\fPa rt 3 : Servos\r\nP roj ec t 1 0 : Joystick-­Co ntrol l ed Laser . . .................. 86\r\nHow It Works........................................................................................ 88\r\nThe Build................................................................................................. 89\r\nMounting the Laser ............................................................................. 90\r\nThe Sketch............................................................................................. 92\r\n\r\nP roj ec t 1 1 : ­Re mote Co n trol Servo............................ 93\r\nHow It Works........................................................................................ 95\r\nThe Setup ................................................................................................ 96\r\nThe Build................................................................................................. 97\r\nThe Sketch............................................................................................. 99\r\n\r\nPa rt 4 : LCDs\r\nP roj ec t 1 2 : LCD Scr e e n W\r\n­ r iter.................................... 102\r\nHow It Works....................................................................................... 104\r\nPreparing the LCD Screen................................................................ 104\r\nthe Build................................................................................................ 105\r\nThe Sketch............................................................................................ 107\r\n\r\nP roj ec t 1 3 : W e ath e r Stati o n.