14	4	JAVA Projects		Java	t	C:\\xampp\\htdocs\\Public_library_codebase\\storage\\uploads\\documents\\4\\31557d9d0bd635dc620e3ec567a7b37a.pdf	\N	2026-04-29 04:08:08.454355	JAVA Projects\r\nIdentify all the problems SJI campus faces in satisfying its students. Propose 3 solutions for\r\neach.\r\nProjects:\r\n1. Campus communication and notification app: Push notifications for timetables, results,\r\nannouncements, could integrate with WhatsApp.\r\n2. Digital library and e-learning platform: Online access to books, lecture notes, and\r\nresearch materials: Can integrate plagiarism checker for student projects.\r\n3. Examination and result management system: Automate exam scheduling, grading and\r\nresult publishing, include GPA calculation and transcript generation.\r\n4. Alumni and career services platform: Connect graduates with employers and track\r\ninternship opportunities, could also include mentorship between alumni and current\r\nstudents.\r\n5. Student examination center.\r\n6. Staff and human resource management statement: Track work load of lecturers.\r\n7. School hosting service: Provides\r\n8. E-payment and financial tracking system: Generate receipt, send reminders\r\n\r\nProject\r\n\r\nDescription\r\n\r\nMembers\r\n\r\nCampus\r\ncommunication and\r\nnotification app\r\n\r\nPush notifications for timetables, results,\r\nannouncements, could integrate with\r\nWhatsApp\r\n\r\nTsehoule\r\nBlondel, Kana\r\nErika\r\n\r\nDigital library and elearning platform\r\n\r\nOnline access to books, lecture notes, and\r\nresearch materials. Can integrate plagiarism\r\nchecker for student projects\r\n\r\nOceanne\r\nAminata, Aloma\r\nXavier\r\n\r\nExamination and\r\nresult management\r\nsystem\r\n\r\nAutomate exam scheduling, grading and\r\nresult publishing, include GPA calculation\r\nand transcript generation.\r\n\r\nSob Fred, Nke\r\nOnana\r\n\r\nAlumni and career\r\nservices platform\r\n\r\nConnect graduates with employers and track\r\ninternship opportunities, could als